  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 45-2-1, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REVISE THE DEFINITION OF THE TERM \"CAUSE OF DEATH\"; TO DELETE LANGUAGE THAT PROHIBITED THE PAYMENT FROM THE LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS AND FIRE FIGHTERS DEATH BENEFITS TRUST FUND WHERE THE DEATH WAS THE RESULT OF SUICIDE OR INTENTIONALLY SELF-INFLICTED BODILY INJURY; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
